articles.description: Up to 20 lawsuits involving houses of worship in states including Nevada, New Jersey, California and Oregon could be influenced by the high-court decision, legal experts say.
articles.content:
The Supreme Court ruling that blocked New York from imposing strict limits on attendance at religious services could influence lawsuits in other states seeking to overturn similar rules on houses of worship.

articles.title: Woman resigns after Zoom fail
articles.description: Almost 140 people watched during a meeting as a New Jersey woman mistakenly publicly broadcast a private moment. She’s now resigned.
articles.content:
